1970-01-01 00:30:00 1. firstly, in a large bowl take 2 cup of fried aloo.
2. add 2 tbsp green chutney, 2 tbsp tamarind chutney, ½ tsp chilli powder, ¼ tsp cumin powder, ¼ tsp aamchur, ¼ tsp chaat masala and ¼ tsp salt.
3. also add 1 tbsp coriander, 2 tbsp onion and mix well.
4. finally, enjoy desi style aloo fry recipe as a tea time snack garnished with sev.
